## Waiting for Elements

```ruby
test "waits for ajax loaded content" do
  visit articles_url
  
  click_button "Load More"
  
  # Wait for element to appear
  assert_selector ".article", count: 20, wait: 5
end

test "waits for element to disappear" do
  visit article_url(@article)
  
  click_button "Delete"
  
  # Wait for confirmation to appear
  assert_selector ".confirmation", wait: 2
end
```

